## Rules

1. **Never run gcloud, Cloud Build, Cloud Run, or any GCP CLI without `--project={{PROJECT_ID}}`** (or equivalent: `gcloud config set project {{PROJECT_ID}}` before commands).
2. **Never reference or deploy to any other GCP project.** All Cloud Run services, Cloud Tasks, Firestore, GCS, etc. must be in `{{PROJECT_ID}}`.
3. **Verify project before deploy/build:** If a script or command does not explicitly set the project, add `--project={{PROJECT_ID}}` or ensure the script sets `gcloud config set project {{PROJECT_ID}}` at the start.
